snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Meet The Team
snippet.description:
Minecraft Dungeons is a new action-adventure game set in the Minecraft Universe and developed by a passionate team. But who are they? What is it like working with a new Minecraft game? And what exactly is “butterfingers”? Go behind the blocks and meet a well-oiled machine of developers that can’t wait to bring you the next installment in the Minecraft franchise.

For more information how you can sign up for a change to play Minecraft Dungeons first, visit https://www.minecraft.net/dungeons
